  <summary date="2022-03-14T18:18:52Z" status="Introduced in Senate">National Commission on the COVID-19 Pandemic Act

This bill temporarily establishes the National Commission on the COVID-19 Pandemic in the legislative branch to investigate the facts and circumstances regarding the emergence of, spread of, and response to COVID-19. The commission terminates 90 days after it submits a final report of its findings and recommendations.</summary>
